<subSubSection lastPageId="7" lastPageNumber="8" pageId="6" pageNumber="7" type="description">
<paragraph blockId="6.[189,529,1776,1802]" box="[189,529,1776,1802]" pageId="6" pageNumber="7">
<heading bold="true" box="[189,529,1776,1802]" fontSize="11" level="3" pageId="6" pageNumber="7" reason="3">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[189,529,1776,1802]" pageId="6" pageNumber="7">Justification of the transfer</emphasis>
</heading>
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="6.[189,1399,1823,2027]" lastBlockId="7.[189,1399,267,329]" lastPageId="7" lastPageNumber="8" pageId="6" pageNumber="7">
Even though we did not examine the 
<typeStatus box="[661,712,1823,1849]" pageId="6" pageNumber="7">type</typeStatus>
of 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Gajbe" authorityYear="1987" box="[760,904,1823,1849]" class="Arachnida" family="Gnaphosidae" genus="Drassyllus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Araneae" pageId="6" pageNumber="7" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="platnicki">
<emphasis box="[760,781,1824,1849]" italics="true" pageId="6" pageNumber="7">D</emphasis>
. 
<emphasis box="[801,904,1823,1849]" italics="true" pageId="6" pageNumber="7">platnicki</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, which may either be lost or misplaced somewhere in the collection, this species agrees with 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Miller" authorityYear="1943" box="[839,1010,1858,1884]" class="Arachnida" family="Gnaphosidae" genus="Cryptodrassus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Araneae" pageId="6" pageNumber="7" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[839,1010,1858,1884]" italics="true" pageId="6" pageNumber="7">Cryptodrassus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
spp. in generic features such as obliquely placed, large, contiguous PMEs, cheliceral promargin with three and retromargin with single tooth and epigyne with anteriorly placed atrium. All these indicate that this species in fact belongs to 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Miller" authorityYear="1943" box="[189,360,1965,1991]" class="Arachnida" family="Gnaphosidae" genus="Cryptodrassus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Araneae" pageId="6" pageNumber="7" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[189,360,1965,1991]" italics="true" pageId="6" pageNumber="7">Cryptodrassus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
. The structure of vulvae of this species looks closely similar to the vulvae of 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Sankaran &amp; Caleb &amp; Sebastian" authorityYear="2020" baseAuthorityName="Tikader &amp; Gajbe" baseAuthorityYear="1976" box="[1257,1399,1965,1992]" class="Arachnida" family="Gnaphosidae" genus="Cryptodrassus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Araneae" pageId="6" pageNumber="7" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="khajuriai" status="comb. nov.">
<emphasis box="[1257,1399,1965,1992]" italics="true" pageId="6" pageNumber="7">C. khajuriai</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
<taxonomicNameLabel box="[189,328,2001,2027]" pageId="6" pageNumber="7" rank="species">comb. nov.</taxonomicNameLabel>
, suggesting a possible synonymy of the former species with the latter one (compare 
<figureCitation box="[189,258,267,294]" captionStart="Fig" captionStartId="2.[189,232,1897,1923]" captionTargetBox="[198,1388,467,1853]" captionTargetId="figure@2.[189,1398,456,1863]" captionTargetPageId="2" captionText="Fig. 1. Cryptodrassus khajuriai (Tikader &amp; Gajbe, 1976) comb. nov., ♀, holotype of Drassyllus khajuriai Tikader &amp; Gajbe, 1976 (NZC-ZSI-5043/18). A. Habitus, dorsal view. B. Eyes of the same, dorsal view. C. Epigyne, ventral view. D. Same, dorsal view. E. Label from type bottle. Scale bars: A = 1 mm; B = 0.5 mm; C–D = 0.2 mm." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3908347" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/3908347/files/figure.png" pageId="7" pageNumber="8">Figs 1</figureCitation>
C–D, 2C–D with 
<bibRefCitation author="Gajbe U. A." box="[475,617,267,294]" pageId="7" pageNumber="8" pagination="289 - 290" refId="ref4905" refString="Gajbe U. A. 1987. A new Drassyllus spider from India (Araneae: Gnaphosidae). Bulletin of the Zoological Survey of India 8: 289 - 290." type="journal article" year="1987">Gajbe 1987</bibRefCitation>
: figs 3–4); however, confirmation requires the examination of the 
<typeStatus box="[189,240,303,329]" pageId="7" pageNumber="8">type</typeStatus>
or topotype materials of 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Sankaran &amp; Caleb &amp; Sebastian" authorityYear="2020" baseAuthorityName="Sankaran &amp; Caleb &amp; Sebastian" baseAuthorityYear="1987" box="[535,672,303,329]" class="Arachnida" family="Gnaphosidae" genus="Drassyllus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Araneae" pageId="7" pageNumber="8" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="platnicki" status="comb. nov.">
<emphasis box="[535,555,303,329]" italics="true" pageId="7" pageNumber="8">C</emphasis>
. 
<emphasis box="[569,672,303,329]" italics="true" pageId="7" pageNumber="8">platnicki</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
<taxonomicNameLabel box="[679,809,303,329]" pageId="7" pageNumber="8" rank="species">comb. nov.</taxonomicNameLabel>
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection pageId="7" pageNumber="8" type="discussion">
<paragraph blockId="7.[189,303,368,394]" box="[189,303,368,394]" pageId="7" pageNumber="8">
<heading bold="true" box="[189,303,368,394]" fontSize="11" level="3" pageId="7" pageNumber="8" reason="3">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[189,303,368,394]" pageId="7" pageNumber="8">Remarks</emphasis>
</heading>
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="7.[189,1398,414,476]" pageId="7" pageNumber="8">
We were unable to find the 
<typeStatus box="[507,558,415,441]" pageId="7" pageNumber="8">type</typeStatus>
of 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Sankaran &amp; Caleb &amp; Sebastian" authorityYear="2020" baseAuthorityName="Sankaran &amp; Caleb &amp; Sebastian" baseAuthorityYear="1987" box="[595,733,414,440]" class="Arachnida" family="Gnaphosidae" genus="Drassyllus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Araneae" pageId="7" pageNumber="8" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="platnicki">
<emphasis box="[595,733,414,440]" italics="true" pageId="7" pageNumber="8">D. platnicki</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
in the arachnid collection of ZSI, even though the author claimed that the 
<typeStatus box="[384,435,450,476]" pageId="7" pageNumber="8">type</typeStatus>
was deposited here (
<bibRefCitation author="Gajbe U. A." box="[680,822,450,476]" pageId="7" pageNumber="8" pagination="289 - 290" refId="ref4905" refString="Gajbe U. A. 1987. A new Drassyllus spider from India (Araneae: Gnaphosidae). Bulletin of the Zoological Survey of India 8: 289 - 290." type="journal article" year="1987">Gajbe 1987</bibRefCitation>
).
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
